{"tid":1393872,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"掟嘢既物理學","createTime":"2019-08-01T08:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T11:51:38.000Z","uid":193026,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8a11eacf65350771c74f69e2f5a2b025b66def93","tid":1393872,"uid":193026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:32:19.000Z","msg":"其實人體結構，係好適合掟嘢<br />\n要用晒咁多結構，簡單講：<br />\n1. 側身對住你要掟既方向<br />\n2. 拎住要掉既物體，扭腰令自己背離目標，同時拎任物體隻手，都背離目標fing<br />\n3. 一口氣向住目標方向扭腰，手向目標方向fing，同時放手fing物體向目標<br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs-prod.si-cdn.com/4ls0fmKgdDQnfArIIdj2npLMDp4=/fit-in/1072x0/https://public-media.si-cdn.com/filer/dc/23/dc2375f9-a924-44fc-bd4f-f2ab9c8c65c4/throwside2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs-prod.si-cdn.com%2F4ls0fmKgdDQnfArIIdj2npLMDp4%3D%2Ffit-in%2F1072x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fpublic-media.si-cdn.com%2Ffiler%2Fdc%2F23%2Fdc2375f9-a924-44fc-bd4f-f2ab9c8c65c4%2Fthrowside2.gif&h=7b3ce9b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係呢個狀態時，將舊物體連手臂向你背後fing<br />\n手臂，膊頭要拉住原本向第二個方向直線飛既物體circular motion（或者離心力，如果方便你理解的話），於是會拉長，好似橡根咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wuPPNDu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwuPPNDu.png&h=a3221710&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後一fing向前時，突然唔再circular motion會令到隻手同膊頭回復原狀，於是會收縮，令舊物體原先fing既相反方向（即係向你要掉既方向）加速<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FnCqkZp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFnCqkZp.png&h=7f379ba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時條腰係全身最強大既肌肉，再用埋條腰既力，令手臂，膊頭fing更大力"},{"pid":"0375b4e11ffa67e97816767b4be96bc7b1edc3c4","tid":1393872,"uid":149607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:34:04.000Z","msg":"清好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213313c29194e94451353ae9688441ecc458614d","tid":1393872,"uid":149607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:34:53.000Z","msg":"乜鬼野程式黎 個skull好撚過癮 幾年前好似用過"},{"pid"