0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl52jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=e2e33b38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://dx.doi.org/10.1038/nature12267</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.smithsonianmag.com/science-nature/how-the-human-body-evolved-to-throw-fastballs-2953790/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smithsonianmag.com%2Fscience-nature%2Fhow-the-human-body-evolved-to-throw-fastballs-2953790%2F&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl52jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=aaea65a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/science-nature/how-the-human-body-evolved-to-throw-fastballs-2953790/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />thanks"},{"pid":"87122dc7a904c8f291e1908ae3c4701d019f332f","tid":1393872,"uid":193026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:43:41.000Z","msg":"另外想講<br />\n一個轉緊既circular motion system（即係你拎住舊物體既腰連手臂）<br />\nangular acceleration不變（你扭腰一樣咁快）<br />\nradius會同velocity成正比（你手臀越長，fing出去果下愈快）<br />\n<br />\n搵繩再駁長舊物體，掉出去時會更高速<br />\n（不過會再用力咗，另外綁實，小心掉掉下甩咗）"},{"pid":"084569a8a23492fb1710f6eb0ce3430a262b4273","tid":1393872,"uid":193026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87122dc7a904c8f291e1908ae3c4701d019f332f","tid":1393872,"uid":193026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:43:41.000Z","msg":"另外想講<br />\n一個轉緊既circular motion system（即係你拎住舊物體既腰連手臂）<br />\nangular acceleration不變（你扭腰一樣咁快）<br />\nradius會同velocity成正比（你手臀越長，fing出去果下愈快）<br />\n<br />\n搵繩再駁長舊物體，掉出去時會更高速<br />\n（不過會再用力咗，另外綁實，小心掉掉下甩咗）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:51:38.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}